  • Constructor Details

    • DragPointCommand

      public DragPointCommand(int dx, int dy, IPoint draggedPoint, IPoint deletedPoint, IPointSet pointSet)
      Instantiates a new drag point command. If the point set contains a point, which has the same coordinated as the dragged point after the dragging, this point is deleted from the point set.
      Parameters:
      dx - the dx
      dy - the dy
      draggedPoint - the dragged point
      deletedPoint - the eventually deleted point
      pointSet - the point set
